    "Limitations and Threats to ValidityFor CyberMetric-10000, most of the questions have been validated by human experts.",
    "However, there remains the possibility of incorrect validations or the presence of irrelevant questions.",
    "Updates and corrections will be announced on the project's website: https://github.com/CyberMetric.",
    "Ethical ConsiderationsThe documents used in this study are publicly accessible via internet searches.",
